# CODEOWNERS — Automatic Reviewer Assignment
#
# This file defines who owns and reviews changes to different parts of the repository.
# When a PR touches files matching these patterns, the listed owners are automatically
# requested for review.
#
# Syntax: <file-pattern> <@github-username> <@github-team>
# Multiple owners can be specified for redundancy and faster reviews.

# Global Ownership
# All files default to the primary maintainer
* @alirezarezvani

